#

Chunky Guacamole with Tomatoes

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackEasy

Description

A fresh and creamy dip bursting with flavor, perfect for snacking or as a topping!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • ripe tomatoes: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
